sequenceDiagram
  autonumber
  participant E as evaluation.run
  participant R as rag.retrieve
  participant L as Azure LLM auditor
  participant M as MCDA

  loop per scenario
    E->>R: retrieve evidence chunks
    E->>L: extract facts, THEN score 5 criteria
    Note over L: fact-first order counters positivity bias
    L-->>E: Assessment + source_chunk_ids
  end
  E->>M: compute_ahp_weights (Saaty consistency ratio)
  E->>M: compute_topsis - rank scenarios
  M-->>E: final_analysis.json + traceability report
